```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 📘 OFFSET

OFFSET skips rows before displaying results.

## Syntax

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Employee
ORDER BY Salary DESC
LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1;
```

Meaning

```text
Skip First Row

↓

Display Next Row
```

Output

```text
Suna
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 📘 Second Highest Salary

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Employee
ORDER BY Salary DESC
LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1;
```

Output

```text
